    "body": "## ISSUE 2: Timestamps shown in the next line and overlapping messages if long capital case display name is set\r\n\r\n### Steps:\r\n1. Set a long display name during onboarding, making all letters in a capital case.\r\n2. Send the message in any chat\r\n\r\n### Actual result:\r\nTimestamps are shown in the next line and overlap messages\r\n![image](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/ce68f09f-0b46-4030-b0a9-54f03ac9b96e)\r\n\r\n### Expected result:\r\nPotential solution:\r\n- Timestamps should remain on the same line as the display name\r\n- If there isn't enough space for  the timestamp, it might be more suitable to truncate the display name or the chat key\r\n",
